Unfortunately she isn’t going to be sentenced to jail. You knew this when producing this clicky….

And It’s Yorkshire Terriers rhyming with “sheer” not “liar.” 😉

As a Queenslander, I know she wouldn’t be jailed here, liar or not, nor indeed anywhere, if she pays the fines.

Which she’ll do. 🤬 unfortunately.

It’s sure as hell a shame, a lot of good people are jailed/gaoled, but people like Heard almost never do.🙄
